1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,000
Three days after the python died, the Empress sent her real one.

2
00:00:03,000 --> 00:00:06,000
Lady Lin — by Imperial Edict, you're summoned to Kunning Palace.

3
00:00:06,000 --> 00:00:09,000
My lady... Matron Li never comes here. This is bad.

4
00:00:09,000 --> 00:00:12,000
If I don't go, she'll have her excuse. Let's see what she's got.

5
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:17,000
She wants to crush me with pageantry? I'll dress better than she expects.

6
00:00:17,000 --> 00:00:24,000
From the cold palace to her hall — every step up the power ladder.

7
00:00:24,000 --> 00:00:27,000
Forbidden-art residue detected. Nature unknown. Marked.

8
00:00:27,000 --> 00:00:30,000
No demonic aura here... but something else is.

9
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:36,000
Lady Lin. Long time. I almost forgot the cold palace still housed you.

10
00:00:36,000 --> 00:00:39,000
So many died in there — and yet you look livelier than ever?

11
00:00:39,000 --> 00:00:42,000
How did Madam Liu die? Who killed those demons?

12
00:00:42,000 --> 00:00:45,000
Demons? I'm a frail woman, Your Majesty. How could I?

13
00:00:45,000 --> 00:00:48,000
Good. Lady Lin — you've grown so much sharper.

14
00:00:48,000 --> 00:00:52,000
Matron Li. Send someone to attend her in the cold palace.

15
00:00:52,000 --> 00:00:55,000
Your servant Cuiwei greets the lady. — Mid-tier demon. Stronger than Liu.

16
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:58,000
My lady! The Empress's gift... is a demon?!

17
00:00:58,000 --> 00:01:02,000
I keep her — at least I know what she is. And she'll lead me back to the Empress.

18
00:01:02,000 --> 00:01:10,000
[Dead silence — a shadow stands at the door — no breath]

19
00:01:10,000 --> 00:01:14,000
She doesn't strike. She just listens. — She's gathering intel.

20
00:01:14,000 --> 00:01:17,000
Then watch all you want. I've got nothing but patience.
